//[Reference] 'So I was thinking about how we could improve the local farmlands.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000100=所以我在考虑怎样改善当地的农田。
//[Reference] 'Our first step should be to improve crop yield.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000200=我们的第一步应该是提高作物产量。
//[Reference] 'After that we'll try out this new formula I invented...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000300=之后,我们将尝试我发明的这个新配方...
//[Reference] 'Are you even listening?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000400=你有在听吗？
//[Reference] 'Just the other day I rolled out a new cultivator.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000500=就在前几天,我推出了一台新的耕耘机。
//[Reference] 'I was going to show you but the mayor confiscated it...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000600=我本来打算给你看的,但市长没收了它...
//[Reference] 'And here it would have made your work so much easier too...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000700=这样你的工作也就容易多了...
//[Reference] 'Don't go drinking bottles you find lying around...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000800=别到喝倒在地上的酒瓶里的酒...
//[Reference] 'Some of those chemicals do nasty things to a person.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000900=有些化学物质对人有害。
//[Reference] 'Not that I'm speaking from experience of course...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001000=这当然不是根据我的个人经验说的...
//[Reference] '^c:d03e37;Seedmakers^c:pop; are fantastic aren't they?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001100=^c:d03e37;种子制作器^c:pop; 太棒了,不是吗？
//[Reference] 'Sometimes you can end up with rare variants!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001200=有时你可能会发现罕见的变种!
//[Reference] 'I wonder if I can rig one to produce them more often...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001300=我想知道我能不能有一个能经常使用的种子制作器...
//[Reference] 'Just to be clear...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001400=要知道...
//[Reference] 'It's professor, not doctor.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001500=我是教授,不是医生。
//[Reference] 'Professor ^c:1486b0;{0-name}^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001600=^c:1486b0;{0-name}^c:pop;教授。
//[Reference] 'Don't mix them up.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001700=别弄混了。
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;{0-shopkeep}^c:pop; has been giving me strange looks recently...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001800=^c:1486b0;{0-shopkeep}^c:pop; 最近一直用奇怪的表情看我...
//[Reference] 'Did I do something to cause offence?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001900=我做过什么事冒犯他了吗？
//[Reference] 'I'm a bit sceptical about that magic water...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002000=我对那个魔力水有点怀疑...
//[Reference] 'I don't know where it came from or how it works...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002100=我不知道它来自哪里,也不知道它是如何工作的...
//[Reference] 'But, there's no way magic is a real thing.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002200=但是,肯定不是魔法。
//[Reference] 'How do airships work, you ask?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002300=你问飞艇的工作怎么样了？
//[Reference] 'Well then! That's a fascinating topic.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002400=很好!这是个有趣的话题。
//[Reference] 'You see, we build the hull from an ultralight super-material.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002500=你看,我们用超级超轻材料建立船体。
//[Reference] 'The rotors-'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002600=转子—
//[Reference] 'Wood? What? Where did you hear that?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002700=木头？啥？你从哪儿听来的？
//[Reference] 'It just looks like wood! It's not really wood!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002800=只是看上去像!并不是真的木头!
//[Reference] 'There's no such thing as magic!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002900=没有魔法之类的东西!
//[Reference] 'Rainy days are such a great energy saver!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003000=下雨天可是个节省能源的好天气!
//[Reference] 'I can turn off all my sprinkler systems.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003100=我可以关掉所有的自动喷水灭火系统。
//[Reference] 'The rain does all the watering for me!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003200=下雨可是给我浇足了水!
//[Reference] 'If you want to know how the lights work, I can't help you.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003300=如果你想知道电灯是怎么工作的,我帮不了你。
//[Reference] 'Countless research projects have proven fruitless.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003400=无数的研究项目被证明毫无结果。
//[Reference] 'We disproved the existence of the luminiferous aether.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003500=我们否定了以太的存在。
//[Reference] 'There is no light emitting photon energy source.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003600=也没有发光光子能量源。
//[Reference] 'And it is definitely. Not. Magic.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003700=当然可以肯定的是,绝!对!不!是!魔!法!。
